** Reporting to the Product Support Manager & working with one peer, this position is responsible for the Driver Fatigue Monitoring ** ** System. Duties include ** ** : **   

  * Monitoring the overall performance of a ** driver fatigue monitoring product ** to reduce warranty costs and to meet needs of customers worldwide. 
  * Identifying problems, investigate causes and establish priorities for resolution. 
  * Contributing to NPI (New Product Introduction) team for the setting of serviceability, reliability and durability goals and pilot test program. 
  * Initiating action for product improvement through warranty program preparation to address commercial/business impact of field problems. 
This is a great career opportunity offering you challenging and interesting
work that straddles software, hardware & networks. There are opportunities to
advance your career for those that are strong  
  
